data.description: Has living in a riverfront property been a dream of yours? Now is your chance! Situated on almost a 1/3 of an acre, this home has 84 feet of river frontage!  It is minutes from the charming community of Shady Cove. This 3 bedroom 2 bath home has an open floor plan. 1664 square feet on the main floor in addition to a finished 1456 sq ft. daylight basement with TONS of storage! Step out onto one of two private decks facing the beautiful Rogue River with direct access from the dining room, primary bedroom and basement. Take a short walk down your private steps and drop a line while living your dreams of fishing from your own riverbank. There is ample parking as well as RV parking. Fresh interior and exterior paint, new dishwasher, new carpet on upper deck, and a new roof. River irrigation rights and so much more! Make this your dream home. With your own personal touches, this just might be it!
